fr.lirmm.graphik.graal.homomorphism.forward_checking

Class SimpleFC

  • java.lang.Object
    • fr.lirmm.graphik.util.profiler.AbstractProfilable
      • fr.lirmm.graphik.graal.homomorphism.forward_checking.SimpleFC
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ForwardChecking, Profilable

    public class SimpleFC
extends AbstractProfilable
implements ForwardChecking
    SimpleFC is a simple ForwardChecking implementation for HyperGraph with immediate local checking in one step. It is simple because it does not maintain a list of possible candidats for each variables.
